nodes.text: Anakkonas were enormous snakes that lived on the forest floors of Kashyyyk. They were among the infamous predators feared by Wookiees. Following his escape from Commander Faie, Quinlan Vos encountered an anakkona that he willed to eat Bogey 5632, a clone trooper member of Bogey Squad. The trick was based on an experience Vos had in which Count Dooku demonstrated mental control over a greater krayt dragon.
